# No environment variables are needed for Cloud Functions.
# The Firebase Admin SDK automatically authenticates using the
# service account associated with your Firebase project.
#
# If you ever need custom secrets (e.g., a third-party API key),
# use Firebase Functions secrets:
#   firebase functions:secrets:set SECRET_NAME
#
# Then access it in code via process.env.SECRET_NAME
# See: https://firebase.google.com/docs/functions/config-env
